OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Staying largely dry in the
OL,7,Fafternoon and turning cloudier. Rain
OL,8,Fmay edge into western Dumfries later.
OL,9,FLight winds becoming strong
OL,10,Fsoutheasterlies near western coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy night with rain
OL,13,Fspreading eastwards and becoming heavy
OL,14,Fat times. Rain clearing western areas
OL,15,Fby morning. Winds becoming strong with
OL,16,Fcoastal gales before easing later in
OL,17,Fthe night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
