OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FHeavy rain clearing east in
OL,6,Fthe morning leaving a largely dry day
OL,7,Fwith bright spells and showers in
OL,8,Fevening. Strong winds around west
OL,9,Fcoast with winds strengthening
OL,10,Felsewhere later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday. Sunny
OL,14,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,15,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,16,FTuesday. Winds will be strong with
OL,17,Frisk of gales Sunday, then becoming
OL,18,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
